extends layouts/head.pug

block content
    h1 Metric / Imperial Convertor

    p An node express api that converts between metric and imperial units. Supports the following units:

    ul
        li mi / km
        li gal / l
        li lbs / kg

    h2 Example usage:

    ul
        li /convert?input=4gal
        li /convert?input=1/2km
        li /convert?input=5.4/3lbs
        li /convert?input=kg

    h2 Example return:

    p {"initNum":3.1,"initUnit":"mi","returnNum":4.98895,"returnUnit":"km","string":"3.1 miles converts to 4.98895 kilometers"}

    h2 Example frontend:

    form(action="/convert", method="post")
        input(type="text", placeholder="example 3gal" name="input")
        button(type="submit") Submit

    if conversionObject
        b #{conversionObject.string}
        p #{JSON.stringify(conversionObject)}